name: Thin Line Cobra Paracord Bracelet
description:
550 Paracord appox. 6 to 9 feet depending on wrist size, when deployed. Waterproof, wont rot or mildew.

Also give us your exact wrist size and we will compensate 
Sizes under 7" will get 1/2"- 3/4" and wrist sizes 8" and up will get 3/4" - 1" depending if you want it tight or loose.

All bracelets come with a black buckle unless you specify a color, check under the buckles category to see pictures.

Please specify Inside color, Outside color, and thin line color. Email me at: knottysurprise@gmail.com or use the contact box
